Arjun, kenapa kamu berdiri disana?

00:05:03.511 --> 00:05:04.951
Kemarilah.

00:05:54.231 --> 00:05:55.631
Arjun.

00:07:31.071 --> 00:07:33.951
Celakalah dia!

00:07:34.551 --> 00:07:36.471
